{"tid":1429063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【轉風向】請緊握扶手，全力轉去反美帝","createTime":"2019-08-07T12:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:33:09.000Z","uid":51814,"like":6,"dislike":181,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f8363c85bf5c7b006b15e2da40463c69194c95","tid":1429063,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:00:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">侵侵話我地係暴徒，就俾佢見識下我地有幾暴力。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>對侵侵五大控訴：<br />\n<br />\n自稱反中國第一人<br />\n<br />\n強迫中國購買大量高價農產品<br />\n<br />\n對中國3000億貨品再加10%關税<br />\n<br />\n以行政指令封殺香港盟友伊朗<br />\n<br />\n將中國列為貨幣操控國</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所有勇武行動將目標指向美帝，<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復</span>被英美殖民主義擄掠嘅<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港</span>，在回歸<span style=\"color: gold;\">時代</span>發起文化清洗大<span style=\"color: gold;\">革命</span>，繼續響應林鄭特首口號<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/192346_65431b4aa44f889587f77794aeed787b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F192346_65431b4aa44f889587f77794aeed787b.gif&h=37cb0f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n罷買蘋果等商品，取消花旗銀行户口，熱烈歡迎解放軍入城共同參與，全火力圍堵美國領事館。</span><br />\n<br />\n利申：爱国爱港连登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da85f0a2240fe538d2c4d409a391fdb9a1bf909","tid":1429063,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> <strong>我地要將香港打造成「反美第一城市」</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7e5e1776d61de4e9135a94de21fc06d2ed22e54b","tid":1429063,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:11:38.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"6d2447c94b9365f0b39966fdcd9a409330f44726","tid":1429063,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:25:16.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"0b717c74eff16c52c42bb67bb591baf2726a442d","tid":1429063,"